solution: ```class Solution {
    public int[] transformArray(int[] nums) {
        int zeros = 0;
        for (int n : nums) if ((n & 1) == 0) zeros++;
        int[] res = new int[nums.length];
        for (int i = 0; i < zeros; i++) res[i] = 0;
        for (int i = zeros; i < res.length; i++) res[i] = 1;
        return res;
    }
}```
